sectioned_description.description:
Superb villa with private swimming pool located above the famous Agni Bay. The villa has 3 air-conditioned bedrooms and can sleep up to 7 guests. High quality interiors and amazing views. Sunbeds on the beach included in the rental price.

Villa Regina is a stunning renovated stone-built property. Located above the famous Agni Bay, the villa offers a private swimming pool, 3 bedrooms and magnificent views over the Ionian Sea. Villa Regina can sleep up to 7 guests in stylish and comfortable interiors.

The property is set over 2 levels, joined together via an exterior staircase. The upper one has a double bedroom, a twin bedroom, a lounge, a kitchen, a dining area, and 2 family shower rooms. The ground floor has a double bedroom with en-suite shower room. Extensive balconies provide breathtaking views.

The infinity-style private swimming pool measures 8x5 metres and is provided with sunbeds and shades: the perfect place to relax and refresh while enjoying the views!

INCLUDED IN THE PRICE: air-conditioning, maid service, hand and bath towels, pool towels, free sunbeds on Agni Beach, (please call at owner's Beach Bar at Agni waterfront).

alternate_sectioned_description_for_p3.description:
Superbe villa avec piscine privée située au dessus de la célèbre baie d'Agni. La villa dispose de 3 chambres climatisées et peut accueillir jusqu'à 7 personnes. Intérieurs de haute qualité et une vue imprenable. Chaises longues sur la plage incluses dans le prix de location. 

 Villa Regina est une superbe propriété en pierre rénovée. Située au-dessus de la célèbre baie d'Agni, la villa dispose d'une piscine privée, de 3 chambres et d'une vue magnifique sur la mer Ionienne. La Villa Regina peut accueillir jusqu'à 7 personnes dans des intérieurs élégants et confortables. 

 La propriété est répartie sur 2 niveaux, reliés entre eux par un escalier extérieur. La chambre supérieure comprend une chambre double, une chambre lits jumeaux, un salon, une cuisine, un coin repas et 2 salles de douche familiales. Le rez-de-chaussée comprend une chambre double avec salle de douche attenante. De vastes balcons offrent des vues à couper le souffle. 

 La piscine privée de style infini mesure 8 x 5 mètres et est équipée de transats et de stores: l’endroit idéal pour se détendre et se rafraîchir tout en profitant de la vue! 

 COMPRIS DANS LE PRIX: climatisation, service de nettoyage, serviettes de toilette et de bain, serviettes de piscine, transats gratuits sur Agni Beach (veuillez appeler au Beach Bar du propriétaire, au bord de l'eau d'Agni).
alternate_sectioned_description_for_p3.name: Villa Regina: Au-dessus d'Agni, vues superbes et piscine

sorted_reviews.comments:
To be short and precise we have really enjoyed our stay at Villa Regina. It gave us memorable moments while sitting outside in the evening and looking into the sea. View was magnificent and relaxing one.
Also I want to emphasize that route into this villa is not the simplest one, but you will get used to it quite quickly. It has some steep hills and some sharp turns, but it's manageable. Parking space is quite narrow so consider renting smaller cars as I don't think you will place bigger one there or at least it will be some kind of a game to do that. Villa has everything you need for your stay (they even managed to get us child bed and chair). House has two floors, but they are not connected from the inside. We have considered this as an advantage - it gave some intimacy for our family. We haven't had any issues except the fact that in the last evening hot water disappeared on the first floor, but it wasn't a big deal. To sum up it was a good stay and we had a great week in Villa Regina.

sorted_reviews.comments: The place exceeded our expectations as the view from the villa is truly breathtaking. It is nearby a lovely quiet bay, which is perfect for a more relaxed and calm vacation. The speedy communication of the hosts was excellent, as well as them allowing us to stay longer after the check out time as our flights were late in the evening.

sorted_reviews.comments: This villa has possibly one of the best pools and views of any place we've stayed in, we liked it so much we stayed there twice. The location is lovely, above Agni Bay, it has a large terrace around the pool but it is not as secluded as we like, as it is overlooked by a neighbouring property and the pool area is open to the road and can be seen from an adjacent access path, though neither are especially busy. The road to get there is quite narrow, winding and steep in places and the parking could feel very awkward for non-confident drivers. The house itself is comfortable and well-equipped but has a tricky layout, being on two separate levels with the largest bedroom in the annex by the pool. The kitchen and lounge are well designed, we personally found the style of the bathrooms and bedrooms a bit old-fashioned but everything worked well and we spent most of the time outside anyway. The management team were very responsive and acted quickly to address any problems we had.
We enjoyed our time at Villa Regina - the views from the pool over the bay will stay in our memories for a very long time!
